            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New</h2>
                <ul>
                <li>Improves startup and layout recovery after display and profile changes so icons are less likely to restore in the wrong place after restart.</li>
                <li>Improves crowded menu bar guidance when Visible gets tight and the Second Menu Bar is a better fit.</li>
                <li>Improves runtime validation and release smoke stability for icon movement and Browse Icons activation.</li>
